<p class="MsoNormalM"><b><u>DAY &nbsp;01</u>–</b>&nbsp;Pickup Dehradun Railway
Station Morning&nbsp;<b><u>06:00 Am&nbsp;</u></b>|<b>Drive to Lohajung&nbsp;
Base via Rishikesh&nbsp;</b>, Devparyag, rudarpayarg, karnaparga Lohajung</p>





<p class="MsoNormalM">Drive Distance: 280 km | Duration: 09-10 hours | 7589 ft
-Overnight Stay Hotel at Lohajung – Twin Sharing or Three Sharing-four sharing</p>





<p class="MsoNormalM"><b><u>DAY 02</u></b>&nbsp;– Trek from Lohajung to Bekaltal
Camp 01 | Trek Distance: 06 km | Trek Time: 4/5 hours | Altitude 9,947 ft |
Overnight Stay Camp – Twin Sharing or Three Sharing</p>





<p class="MsoNormalM"><b><u>DAY 03</u></b><u>&nbsp;–</u>&nbsp;Trek from Bekaltal
to Brahmatal Base Camp 02 via Jhandi Top | Trek Distance: 07 km | Trek Time:
6/7 hours | Altitude 10,318 ft | Overnight Stay Camp – Twin Sharing or Three
Sharing</p>





<p class="MsoNormalM"><b><u>DAY 04</u></b>&nbsp;– &nbsp;Early Morning 4:30 am Trek
from &nbsp;Brahmatal &nbsp;Base Camp to&nbsp;<b><i><u>Brahmatal Summit Peak
Summit –</u></i></b>12250 ft &nbsp;|After Summit – Back to Brahmatal Base Camp
– Trek Distance: 05 km | Trek Time : 4/5 hours | Altitude 8,498 ft | Overnight
Stay Camp &nbsp;– Twin Sharing or Three Sharing</p>





<p class="MsoNormalM"><b><u>DAY 05</u></b>&nbsp;– Trek from Brahmatal base&nbsp;
Camp to Lohajung Hotel | Trek Distance: 08 km | Trek Time: 4/5 hours | Altitude
7,589 ft | Overnight Stay Hotel &nbsp;&nbsp;– Twin Sharing or Three Sharing</p>





<p class="MsoNormalM"><b><u>DAY 06</u>&nbsp;</b>– Drive Back from Lohajung to
Dehradun via Rishikesh Drive Distance: 280 km | Drive Duration: 09-10hours
|&nbsp;<b><u>Drop point for Himalayan Hikers trekkers: Dehradun Railway Station</u></b></p>





<p class="MsoNormalM">&nbsp;</p>






