                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>23. Are guides provided?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    Yes, experienced trek leaders and local guides accompany every group.                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>24. Is the trek safe for solo travelers?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    Absolutely. It’s a well-guided group trek with full safety support.                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>25. Is medical assistance available?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    Yes, first-aid kits, oxygen cylinders, and basic medicines are carried.                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>26. Is a mobile network available?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    Limited or no signal during the trek; weak connectivity at Lohajung.                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>27. Is emergency evacuation possible?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    Yes, mules or vehicles can be arranged from the nearest road point.                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>28. How do I reach the base camp (Lohajung)?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    You can reach Lohajung via Rishikesh by shared taxi or private cab (10–11 hours drive).                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>29. Nearest railway station and airport?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    <p><span style="font-weight: bold;">Railway Station:</span> Rishikesh / Haridwar;&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: bold;">Airport:</span> Dehradun (Jolly Grant Airport).</p>                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>30. What’s included in the trek package?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    Stay, 5-time meals per day, guide, permits, equipment, and transport from base to trek start point. Optional: porter, insurance, and personal gear rental at extra cost.                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                                                       </div>
                        </div>
                     </div>
                  </div>
               </div>
